Class DataModelList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<DataModel>
        • edu.cmu.tetrad.data.DataModelList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataModel, KnowledgeTransferable, VariableSource, TetradSerializable, Serializable, Iterable<DataModel>, Collection<DataModel>, List<DataModel>

    public final class DataModelList
extends AbstractList<DataModel>
implements DataModel, TetradSerializable
    Stores a list of data models and keeps track of which one is selected.
    Author:
    Joseph Ramsey jdramsey@andrew.cmu.edu
    See Also:
    DataModel, Serialized Form
